{"tid":1507421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廿多人稅務大樓靜坐 促政府回應5大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:52:03.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17af2dcff7f88c180ac7721eb69cd193bf357b62","tid":1507421,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"有網民今午響應號召前往灣仔稅務大樓靜坐抗議，要求政府回應民間5大訴求，行動約有20多人參與，未對稅務大樓造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n靜坐活動在中午12時開始，有靜坐人士遮蓋左眼，有人舉起「沒有暴徒，只有暴政」標語，高呼「香港警察，污糟邋遢」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">靜坐期間，有途經市民叫「加油」打氣，亦有途人指靜坐人士是「曱甴」，又批評在場記者為「黑媒」。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2230367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2230367%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=ab368606\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2230367/</a>"},{"pid":"5b4fe8f2da3d9e857b6d978f1fae061ab0be9b7d","tid":1507421,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=6f4e410f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"20887d258089ad03bebc0b2ea6f2507098bca801","tid":1507421,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cfd81294bc94c4d331aceae63f06829368d2eb","tid":1507421,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"[9．1機場] 文宣集合 2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://li